description: This dataset merges Kenya's primary school enrollment data (2001–2020) with GDP per capita data from the World Bank.

columns.name: PrimaryEnrollment
columns.meaning: Gross or net primary school enrollment (number of students)

columns.name: GDP_per_capita
columns.meaning: GDP per capita in current USD

notes: Merged on Year and Country. Data covers 2001–2020. Missing values indicate unavailable data.
